cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses machine learning techniques for complex real-world applications with nonuniform testing and misclassification costs, which are common topics in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The title and abstract also mention the induction of low cost low error classifiers, which further supports these sub-categories.
